name: SHKOOBY INU
description: SHKOOBY INU ($SHKOOBY) is a decentralized & community-driven meme token on the Ethereum Blockchain. The Shkooby Metaverse (Shkooby-verse) will feature a Swap, Games, NFTs, and an NFT Marketplace. $SHKOOBY will aim to bring utility across the entire meme-coin universe. We begin with releasing products relevant to our native token, $SHKOOBY, but will immediately proceed with releasing SHKOOBY SWAP, a dedicated farm for dog coings, with the most Shkoobielicious rewards. The SHKOOBY-VERSE will serve as the core ecosystem of SHKOOBY INU. The Metaverse will be for people of all ages and cultures worldwide and will be the future of memes. $SHKOOBY will be the currency of the Metaverse.
